Class EncoderPreprocessor<K,V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.ignite.ml.preprocessing.encoding.EncoderPreprocessor<K,V>
  • Type Parameters:

    Preprocessing function that makes encoding. This a base abstract class that keeps the common fields for all child encoding preprocessors.
